extracted_text:
Chaussettes 2420. Vous avez bien fait de vendre la caisse à 7 ,30 et vendre également que vous avez vendue à 7 ,85.

Bachir Aziz : Reçu la facture pour les trois chaussettes supplémentaires et a déjà encaissé le montant.

Reçu les trente crédits-notes pour le retour des trois caisses à différents clients.

Hussein Sami : Reçu le kifset et la facture pour la caisse n° 2420 S. et nous ferons le recouvrement.

Ahmed Abdel Baki : Reçu la police pour les dix-et-demi gilets, douze livres de coton, et confirme le recouvrement.

Rien à faire, c’est très calme, et tous attendent le commencement des autos. Dès qu’ils ont appris que Rachid est descendu, il a fort ennui ; Abdel veut que ce soit imprimé en trois coups.

Sabah Ferès : Je lui ai vendu et livré et vous prie de m’envoyer la facture pour 10 ½ gilets sport rayé 81 % à 29 …

Hussein Sami : Je lui ai vendu et vous prie de rechercher les réchésas : 3627, 1,5 ; 3629, 5 …

Guigui Hafizal : N’a offert pour chaussettes civiles 8405 à 25.

Flm : a offert pour la caisse neuve, crédit 394, 6,5, par la bâtisse arrivée le 9-6-26. Nous renseignerons.

Sous autre prix ce soir…
Raichende
Translation_to_English:
Socks 2420. You were right to sell the case at 7.30 and also to sell the other one at 7.85.

Bachir Aziz: Invoice received for the three extra socks, and the amount has already been collected.

Received the thirty credit notes for the return of the three cases to various clients.

Hussein Sami: The kifset and the invoice for case No. 2420 S have been received and we will handle the collection.

Ahmed Abdel Baki: The policy for the ten-and-a-half waistcoats, twelve pounds of cotton, has been received and the collection is confirmed.

Nothing to do, it is very calm, and everyone is waiting for the start of the cars. As soon as they learned that Rachid went down, he became very annoyed; Abdel wants it printed in three copies.

Sabah Ferès: I have sold and delivered to him and ask you to send me the invoice for 10 ½ striped sport waistcoats at 81 % for 29 …

Hussein Sami: I have sold to him and ask you to look for the rechésas: 3627, 1.5; 3629, 5 …

Guigui Hafizal: He did not bid for civilian socks 8405 at 25.

Flm: Offered for the new case, credit 394, 6.5, by the building that arrived on 9-6-26. We will inform you.

At another price tonight…
Raichende
